  "description": {
    "main": "The Sony BRAVIA Theatre Bar 8 is all about bringing that big-screen audio right to your sofa. With 360 Spatial Sound Mapping, you're getting a surround sound experience without any extra gear. It's like the audio is coming from everywhere, bouncing off the walls and ceiling for that cinema vibe. And with Sound Field Optimization, the acoustics are not only fine-tuned to your space but where you're sitting. It packs a punch too. The cleverly shaped X-Balanced Speaker Units serve up deep bass and clear vocals with minimal distortion. Plus, it's all geared up for Dolby Atmos, DTS:X and IMAX Enhanced content, so your movie nights are about to get a whole lot more epic.",
    "goodToKnow": [
      "Pair it with your BRAVIA TV to unlock features like Acoustic Centre Sync and Voice Zoom 3",
      "Stream your tunes using Spotify Connect, Apple AirPlay, or Bluetooth",
      "Music sounds oh-so-good with immersive 360 Reality Audio and DSEE Extreme upscaling",
      "Game on with support for VRR, ALLM, plus 8K and 4K120 Passthrough",
      "Add wireless rear speakers for an even bigger sound stage and up to 11 phantom speakers",
      "Setup is easy with the BRAVIA Connect app - tweak the sound, get updates, and even boss your TV around"
    ]
